{"tid":1692598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[同我推上熱門] 監察612基金","createTime":"2019-11-04T07:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T09:34:02.000Z","uid":137109,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b01c57d1298b4768c8c452589db7c2ce97b41a29","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:06:37.000Z","msg":"連登神袐力量令一切檢討612基金post變做分化而沉底<br />\n<br />\n文長 希望大家幫手推+比意見. 再次強調並非割席 亦都絕對相信+肯定你哋為運動出咗好多力 <br />\n但抗爭手足身陷囹圄 好需要資源($+法律)嘅back up 希望你地可以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">善用現有最龐大資源</span></strong></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>捐助者有責任確保資金用於手足上 612funding並非贖罪卷</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基金籌咗<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">8300萬</span></span></strong>有多 至今只用<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">500萬</span></span></strong>, 吳靄儀早前話要預留一筆逾4000萬資助民事索償案件<br />\n<br />\n作為支援抗爭者大型基金 有必要回應香港人質詢 提高透明度 令funding發揮更大作用 主要講司法覆核 透明度 同 理財方面提意見 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(1）<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臨時禁令/司法覆核</span></strong><br />\n司法覆查重要之處在於影響日後所有法律判決/警方行動計劃:<br />\n禁令可以讓弱者受法律明文保護<br />\n連tvb都申請保護記者, 泛民入紙反蒙面法<br />\n作為抗爭基金 點解唔可以代冇深入法律知識嘅抗爭者尋求法律保護? <br />\n好明顯從6月到依家大把唔合理嘅case需要JR/禁止:<br />\n包括但不限於<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">Green object</span></span></strong>: 嗰啲電光火石決定全撚部合法? 一定要向法院覆核<br />\nA. 自帶武裝/改制服 (如黑口罩)<br />\nB. 武裝使用指引 (內部守則,武力對等原則+法律原則）eg. 葵芳地鐵tg, 荃灣/尚德企圖謀殺手足, 新城市報復第四權<br />\nC. 武裝使用後調查報告 (6月前淨係用棍都要寫report. 公眾利益情況下可公開?)<br />\nD. 處理&rdquo;自殺案手法&rdquo;, 死因庭同法醫意見(浮屍處理程序有問題而無法調查)<br />\nE. 執行職務範圍 (入公大開槍/大學範圍甚至糖水鋪拉人真係冇問題?)<br />\nF. 制衡機制: 射盲記者/老師, 新屋嶺性侵, 開實彈<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">法律</span></span></strong><br />\nA. 遊行集會基本人權點解需要不反對， 係咪意味警方可以更高理由凌駕基本人權 而呢啲理由係咩<br />\nB. 藍page起底懸紅網點解唔受規管?<br />\nC. 蒙面法有多手足被48/加控罪名, 立法程序/內容完全冇問題?<br />\nD. 貼文宣本來歸食環管而狗近日拘捕全部合法? <br />\nE. 痴poster 而帶番狗屋扣查合乎程序公義?<br />\nF. 法律面前人人平等點解721唔叫暴動 冇popo/黑社會需要付刑責?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢啲問題正正需要你幫手解答<br />\n結果會係<br />\n(1)幫到手足 +避免日後抗爭者無故受法律程序折磨, 對黑警部署有阻嚇性<br />\n(2) 顯示<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">法治已死, 行動升級, 因判決而促使無限期三罷</span></strong></span><br />\n起碼我地可以搵到個答案 而運動唔係停留喺好嬲, 無力 咩都做唔到 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(2)透明度<br />\nA. 反濫權大控訴合作<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/106143357451269/photos/a.106732540725684/141264750605796/?type=3&amp;source=48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F106143357451269%2Fphotos%2Fa.106732540725684%2F141264750605796%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26source%3D48&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfn5V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=113f77e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/106143357451269/photos/a.106732540725684/141264750605796/?type=3&amp;source=48</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10.23籌夠錢後冇音訊</span></span></strong><br />\n詳情係點? 嗰度一千萬加幾個核彈 至少交代下進度/未來意向? 冇理由籌咗咁耐錢到籌夠先開始plan點入稟掛<br />\n<br />\nB. 項目資助申請<br />\n共9個項目拎咗共800萬 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係法律費用嘅double</span></span></strong><br />\n有需要公開下係咩項目重要過手足開飯錢/前線法律支援/流亡海外手足援助<br />\n<br />\nC. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對上一次工作報告已經兩個月</span></strong> 有需要至少2星期update 下?簡陋少少好過影都冇<br />\n<br />\nD. 咁多樣緊要野唔做 facebook到居然話支援在囚人士買原子筆/探訪家屬交通費?<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=445511529482350&amp;id=368482457185258&amp;anchor_composer=false\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D445511529482350%26id%3D368482457185258%26anchor_composer%3Dfalse&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfn5V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=4f518b2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=445511529482350&amp;id=368482457185258&amp;anchor_composer=false</a><br />\n呢啲細數就算家屬比都冇問題啦 排下優次好冇 有咩重要啱啱講咗 <br />\n<br />\n(3) 財政處理<br />\n1. 守財奴<br />\n你肯洗落有需要嘅人身上 我哋香港人多多都肯捐<br />\n8300-500-4000(預作堂費)= 3000多萬, 絕對綽綽有餘<br />\n<br />\n2. 亂開帳目<br />\n民陣還民陣 612 還612 音響開支應由市民捐比民陣捐款扣除 而唔係612度拎<br />\n612基金&rdquo;是為反送中運動中受傷、被捕或有關人士，提供人道支援&rdquo; (612 website) 麻煩你劃清楚界線。<br />\n叧外參與國際會議費用有冇claim任何基金開支? 請你向公眾尤其有捐款嘅人清楚交代<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n企出嚟啦 香港人需要你嘅幫手！唔夠使我地一定會再捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"4ea9597452ae5b84e78db0bcc647761416820413","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"推上去！"},{"pid":"96a4b0978f48c2315edf23f308c7ccdaaac85aa6","tid":1692598,"uid":32836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:07:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b22ae35b07b3ee314b36275d6e34fb9d4e527cf","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"612出嚟回應下好冇 我哋都係想funding 落到去幫手足"},{"pid":"07a797d0501e2e0c2a00d55230742c16b5ec914e","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:08:36.000Z","msg":"推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898a41de7bfe0b32ddffb0cae49cfe9641acfdf6","tid":1692598,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"077f50c20d1e9eb212a616325b37e9cd5404cf67","tid":1692598,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"基金比例真係用得太少。如果做守財奴，點解市民唔將錢擺係自己度。"},{"pid":"5ef8e036312135ba6968882e1071e4cefd093ffd","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捐完錢都要監察"},{"pid":"1fa6fa6bbd6b19768a239ee7d421d80ad408446c","tid":1692598,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e5e87f4dae9f3464ddfcf21dd683e44c1bb972","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"077f50c20d1e9eb212a616325b37e9cd5404cf67","tid":1692598,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"基金比例真係用得太少。如果做守財奴，點解市民唔將錢擺係自己度。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者比其他funding 星火冇公開盤數但係我哋信得過佢有善用資源"},{"pid":"f44025bc008732e136934f13b2c50045c466b59d","tid":1692598,"uid":121985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"8a19bf5636950b38a72910736cdd1d237070c741","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:14:06.000Z","msg":"神秘負皮入嚟駁下嘴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />交流下意見"},{"pid":"f938e0f04dfb9b6891a41d7b6e28d9f2f80d9abf","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"推上去 講得唔好入嚟屌柒我"},{"pid":"8e73347ba0c2449ae40f087035c34889e089f4c9","tid":1692598,"uid":319434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"輕輕推<br />\n好多𡃁仔𡃁妹驚麻煩到人唔敢攞sup<br />\n原來612收埋咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4da0185fd04d7143dd169252a7eacb35a20d321","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"又沉落水底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ee08dbde06a52b36c9e9e77fe6279328e24284","tid":1692598,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"c098a24420414bf99ee5f7b2c10db72d7b6561fb","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e73347ba0c2449ae40f087035c34889e089f4c9","tid":1692598,"uid":319434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:14:58.000Z","msg":"輕輕推<br />\n好多𡃁仔𡃁妹驚麻煩到人唔敢攞sup<br />\n原來612收埋咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"唔完美 可改善 需要監察<br />\n612要做好多嘢令人重拾信心"},{"pid":"5b56420566d1cb08288639aa621035478bdedcf4","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"拜托推上去"},{"pid":"6a86fdeae6869b1e9c4d30be7afb41edcf7fae40","tid":1692598,"uid":154882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cd65bdf6011cbb151cc90b9ad0e865eb63c2f9","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:19:24.000Z","msg":"負皮有冇睇哂成篇野"},{"pid":"2bd6c1089cd878a5bc7b2fd879b15c587ecc56ec","tid":1692598,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d52c49511764cfc8fe8d542ed34dfe2450334c0","tid":1692598,"uid":40745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"612本質上係要輸左先有用既基金，贏左洗撚咁多法律支援。"},{"pid":"5e3992c1a88214fc447d7d5f83178317df6f4d0f","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d52c49511764cfc8fe8d542ed34dfe2450334c0","tid":1692598,"uid":40745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"612本質上係要輸左先有用既基金，贏左洗撚咁多法律支援。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"司法覆核<br />\n之後同類案件會參照覆核結果 eg tg可以係咩情況放"},{"pid":"2503f448f6c0a13f74fe07105856c254423f43d2","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:22:38.000Z","msg":"又唔見咗個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29c83be6abaf7d8f0c5feefabd76f45fdab9c15","tid":1692598,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:24:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/List.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp3.legco.gov.hk%2Fors%2Fchinese%2FList.aspx&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfn5V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=8488c100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app3.legco.gov.hk/ors/chinese/List.aspx</a>"}]}